{
  "stem": "5970.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I-- I can't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I did come back to the ghetto eventually, when that was-- that place was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And all the people-- they kept the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But the Jewish people, they dismissed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were all sent to different-- different camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I was sent back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And at that stage, the ghetto was very small.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Most of the people were sent away already by 1943, and-- to different concentration camps, to death camps, and to everywhere else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There was just a very small workshop in which both my parents worked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my little sister was still with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My younger brother was sent somewhere away, somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "My older brother was already dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So there were just the four of us left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they both worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My little sister didn't work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I was sent back to work in that workshop where my parents were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I was given a job in a-- they had-- they had a shirt factory there that they made shirts for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a shoe works, and my father was busy there; and some other workshops, I can't remember exactly what it was-- some leather things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but I-- I remember what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in charge of that workshop were two men, not from Radom, funnily enough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were experts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The one had a shirt factory in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember even their names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they were nice, very lovely people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were so patient with us, the youngsters that were looking there, and showing us everything, and-- and helping us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we really didn't have a clue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was a-- a new thing all together, to-- to make shirts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't sew them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We folded them.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
